I was a little skeptical - what with canned tuna and oranges, a seemingly unlikely pair! But, we're trying to lose some weight and this recipe fit within our criteria so I gave it a try. WOW! It was fantastic. The dressing really enhances the dry tuna and the little bits of orange provide bursts of juicy sweetness. Not only would I make this again, I'd pay for it in a restaurant!

