Loved this, as did the gals in my book club. It was a leeetle liquidy but a slotted spoon for serving solved that. I added a cooked purple potato and used green olives with no pimiento. The potato was nice to help balance the sweetness of the orange, pepper & red wine vinegar. Perfect for summer (no heat!). I felt lively and healthy and like a million bucks after eating this meal.

