Rating: 4
Made my own variation of this for dinner last night. Used roasted red peppers instead of raw, and seared two tuna steaks as opposed to canned letting the other ingredients (except greens) sit in the dressing as tuna cooked. Piled the greens on a platter, topped with the sliced tuna, and finished it off with the dressing. Delicious and very attractive on the plate. Will definitely be making this one again!

